{{DISPLAYTITLE:Soul Blazer:RAM map}}
This is the '''RAM map''' for '''[[Soul Blazer]]''' (SNES).

==Overview==
Soul Blazer uses SNES Work RAM ($7E0000-$7FFFFF) for game state, with battery-backed SRAM for save data.

